title: Creative Nail UV Lamp 110 Volt
description: CND's UV Lamp is engineered for a complete cure with maximum wearability. This powerful versatile, and ergonomic UV lamp is perfect for both Shellac and Brisa Gel nail services. Four 9-watt bubls deliver 36 watts of evenly distributed cure. Ideal for both a five-finger cure or a pdiecure, the lamp contains four programmable timers, an interior fan and bulb replacement indicator. With a seven-foot removable cord, a comfortable handle for easy transport, an easy-to-clean surface and a one-year warranty, what more couldy ou ask for?

title: Creative Nail Shellac, Iced Coral, 0.25 Fluid Ounce
description: Just the icing on top. A beautiful light pink/coral shade packed with green and gold shimmer. CND's Iced Coral Shellac coats your beautiful manicure like smooth and delicious icing on a cake. This UV cured color coat applies on like polish, wears like a gel, but can be removed in minutes. Creat 14 days of superior color, no matter what you and your nails go through in a day. Simply set it and forget it. Improve your nails with a pratical and fearless armor color coat.
